      td üü° Active development, functional prototype phase next.
    tr
      td: h4 Kapybara PRO
      td üî¥ Not being developed at the moment / development will start later.

  hr
  p Thanks for the support! ü§ç <br>- MMM (Marcos, Maria, and Michael)
